Version 0.0.3 - Released 2008/05/17
===================================

FULL CHANGES
------------

 - First working version

 - os_gentoo provides the required tools to manage
   /etc/portage/package.*

 - service_openldap installs openldap now.


SHORT CHANGES
-------------

 p@rdalys-0.0.3 is a first working version of the package. It is
 capable of managing some basic aspects of Gentoo (primarily the
 /etc/portage/package.* files/directories) and installs an
 experimental version of openldap.


